@DATABASE "Alien Evolution"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - A - Alien Evolution"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - A
                   ====================================

                              Alien Evolution
                              ===============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(58228,0)"}          58228,0
@{"Infinite Time " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(61527,0)"}          61527,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(61970,0)"}          61970,0 (x= 1-255)
@{"Time = x      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(61824,0)"}          61824,0 (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
